text: The Papua New Guinea women's national soccer team, nicknamed the Lakatois, represents Papua New Guinea in international women's soccer. It is controlled by the Papua New Guinea Football Association (PNGFA). ==Related pages== * Papua New Guinea national soccer team * Soccer in Papua New Guinea ==References== Soccer Category:Oceanian women's national football teams Category:Soccer in Papua New Guinea Category:Sports organisations of Papua New Guinea
